		<category><![CDATA[Venture Capital]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://ventureburn.com/?p=199777</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>MillTech secured $60 million of additional funding from Apax Digital Funds, the growth equity practice of the leading venture capital group, Apax Partners. The investment placed the equity value at</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/milltech-bags-60m-to-scale-treasury-and-fx-tools/" data-wpel-link="internal">MillTech Bags $60M to Scale Treasury and FX Tools</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://milltech.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400">MillTech </span></a><span style="font-weight: 400">secured $60 million of additional funding from Apax Digital Funds, the growth equity practice of the leading </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/eclipse-ventures-1-3b/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">venture capital</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> group, Apax Partners. The investment placed the equity value at around $325 million, which is an important step in the company&#8217;s deep growth mindset.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">MillTech offers a technology platform that enables corporations and investment managers with large cash flows to better manage FX hedging and cash management. Its technology automates all key FX lifecycle processes, from trade calculations and decision-making to execution, settlement and reporting.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">A typical multi-bank FX risk management process involves a number of brokers and broken-down functions. MillTech offers a direct connection with its clients to the wholesale multi-bank market, a solution that offers better transparency and execution.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Pooling liquidity across multiple banking partners enables the platform to enable companies to hedge currency exposure with greater efficiency and less complexity. According to the company, its technology can lower FX execution costs by over 50% versus a traditional banking structure.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">AI-Powered Treasury Tools</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The funding focuses on developing artificial intelligence features within the platform. </span><span style="font-weight: 400">MillTech has been developing a suite of tools based on AI that ingest market data to provide optimised hedging strategies and enhanced risk management insights to clients, supporting improved decision-making on the timing and method of hedging currency exposure.</span></p>
<div id="attachment_199780" style="width: 1034px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-199780" class="size-large wp-image-199780" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/FX-market-on-phone-screen-1024x683.jpg" alt="FX market on phone screen" width="1024" height="683" /><p id="caption-attachment-199780" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Unsplash</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">As the harnessing of data and automation within financial institutions spreads, AI treasury solutions will become an integral part of the modern financial infrastructure. MillTech hopes to position itself as a cutting-edge platform for corporate treasury teams and institutional investors by incorporating the aforementioned technologies.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">More News: </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/eclipse-ventures-1-3b/" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">Eclipse Ventures Raises $1.3B to Advance Physical AI Startups</span></a></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">Expanding Into North America</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Another primary goal of the funding round is expansion into the United States and broader North American market. North America represents a major opportunity for FX risk management platforms because multinational companies in the region manage significant cross-border currency exposure.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">According to MillTech CEO Eric Huttman, the new investment will help the company accelerate this growth strategy while continuing to build advanced treasury solutions. The partnership with Apax, he noted, validates the platform’s long-term potential and market demand.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">Investors&#8217; Confidence</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company&#8217;s investment is representative of a trend: the increase in demand for a high-tech way to handle the fluctuations in currency values. The global foreign exchange (FX) market sees an estimated 9.5 trillion dollars in daily currency trading, a number that accentuates the importance of FX risk management for companies.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">MillTech has exhibited excellent momentum in the recent past. The company posted 79% revenue growth in 2024 and 73% in 2025, which is indicative of the swift uptake of its technology by institutional investors.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The platform processes $500 billion of trading each year, enabling institutional investors and corporate clients to hedge billions of dollars worth of currency exposure.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Apax Digital Funds, which led the investment, is already familiar with the platform. Apax has previously used MillTech’s technology across several of its funds to support investment operations, making the new deal both a strategic partnership and a financial investment.</span></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/milltech-bags-60m-to-scale-treasury-and-fx-tools/" data-wpel-link="internal">MillTech Bags $60M to Scale Treasury and FX Tools</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
			</item>
